panels.name: Detected Events
panels.queryString:
$$AQUASEC_SOURCE_CATEGORY
| json field=_raw "result" | where %result = 3 | count by result

panels.name: Blocked Events
panels.queryString: | parse "\"user\":\"*\",\"action\":\"*\",\"image\":\"*\",\"host\":\"*\",\"category\":\"*\",\"result\":2" as user, action, image, host, category | count

panels.name: Running Disallowed Images
panels.queryString:
$$AQUASEC_SOURCE_CATEGORY
| json field=_raw "image", "category", "result", "host", "reason" as image, category, result, host, reason
| where %result = 2 AND %category="image" AND %reason matches "*Unauthorized*"
| count by image, host

panels.name: Total Events
panels.queryString: | parse "\"user\":\"*\",\"action\":\"*\",\"image\":\"*\",\"host\":\"*\",\"category\":\"*\"" as user, action, image, host, category | count

panels.name: Image Assurance - Policy Disallowed
panels.queryString:
$$AQUASEC_SOURCE_CATEGORY
| json field=_raw "image", "category", "result", "action", "data" as image, category, result, action, data
| json field=data "policy_name", "controls" as policy, controls
| where %category = "image" AND %result=4 AND %action = "policy.failure"
| count by policy

panels.name: Top 20 High Severity Images
panels.queryString:
$$AQUASEC_SOURCE_CATEGORY
| json field=_raw "image", "category","high" as image, category, high
| where %category = "CVE" AND high > 0
| sort by high desc
| top 20 image by high
| first(image) as image group by image, high
| sum(high) by high, image
| fields -high

panels.name: Network Events
panels.queryString:
$$AQUASEC_SOURCE_CATEGORY
| json field=_raw "action", "category", "image", "resource", "host", "result" | where %action = "connect" AND %category = "network"
| if(result = "2", "Block", result) as result
| if(result = "3", "Detect", result) as result
| count by image, resource, host, result
| order by result asc

panels.name: Failed Host Logins
panels.queryString:
$$AQUASEC_SOURCE_CATEGORY
| json field=_raw "user", "host","command","action", "result" as user, host, command, action, result 
| where %action = "login" AND %result=2 
| count by user, host, command 
| top 20 user, host, command by _count 
| sort by _count desc

panels.name: Top 5 Blocked Actions
panels.queryString: | parse "\"user\":\"*\",\"action\":\"*\",\"image\":\"*\",\"host\":\"*\",\"category\":\"*\",\"result\":2" as user, action, image, host, category | count by action, image | sort by action, image
